<h3>Return Policy:</h3>
</p>
<p>
Our main goal is to satisfy our customers. Our return policy tries to be as accommodating as possible during this process. We do strive for a 100% quality standard. If you feel that your item is defective, you should contact us within the warranty period for a possible exchange or refund. We will issue and RMA#, return merchandise authorization number.  
</p>
<p>
